description: This file declares external API functions related to a Simple Proxy TCP object within the Advanced Networking Service Container (ANSC) framework. It includes prototypes for creating, removing, enrolling, and initializing such objects.

methods.name: AnscCreateSimpleProxyTcp
methods.description: Creates a new instance of the Simple Proxy TCP object with specified container, owner, and reserved contexts.

methods.name: AnscSptoCreate
methods.description: Creates a new Simple Proxy TCP object instance with provided container, owner, and reserved handles.

methods.name: AnscSptoRemove
methods.description: Removes/deletes the specified Simple Proxy TCP object instance.

methods.name: AnscSptoEnrollObjects
methods.description: Enrolls or registers necessary objects for the Simple Proxy TCP instance.

methods.name: AnscSptoInitialize
methods.description: Initializes the Simple Proxy TCP object instance.
